OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773227361
OL,3,CWarrington MP tells Parliament she was
OL,4,Craped while at a work event
OL,6,FAn MP has waived her anonymity to tell
OL,7,FParliament she was raped while in her
OL,8,Frole.
OL,10,FLabour's Warrington North
OL,11,Frepresentative Charlotte Nichols, who
OL,12,Fhas not previously spoken in the
OL,13,FCommons about her experience, said it
OL,14,Fhappened at an event she attended as a
OL,15,Fmember of Parliament.
OL,17,FShe shared her story as she hit out at
OL,18,Fthe Deputy Prime Minister David
OL,19,FLammy's plans to curb access to jury
OL,20,Ftrials as MPs debated the Courts and
OL,21,FTribunals Bill.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
